# Testing Gates

- Any module change must include matching unit test coverage updates.
- Validate at least create/update/delete/idempotency/check-mode or info-module filters.
- Run formatting and sanity checks before finalizing:
  - `make check-format`
  - `make new-sanity`
  - `make test:unit`
- Do not merge module changes that skip unit tests.
